      <title>瑞银：新冠疫情爆发以来亿万富翁移民频率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/billionaires-emigrating-more-frequently-since-covid-ubs-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自新冠疫情爆发以来，亿万富翁越来越频繁地移居新的国家，主要目的地包括瑞士、阿联酋、新加坡和美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/billionaires-emigrating-more-frequently-since-covid-ubs-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国亿万富翁的 RoyalFlush 交易应用程序是刺激计划的最大赢家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/china-billionaire-yi-zheng-s-royalflush-trading-app-is-big-winner-of-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自9月份国家推出刺激计划以来，中国皇家同花顺 (RoyalFlush) 交易应用程序背后的大亨的财富增加了 60 亿美元，凸显出波动性对少数精英阶层来说是一种福音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/china-billionaire-yi-zheng-s-royalflush-trading-app-is-big-winner-of-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>HPS 向贝莱德出售后提供激励措施以留住员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hps-offers-incentives-to-retain-staff-after-sale-to-blackrock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻看到的一封投资者信显示，HPS Investment Partners 将向员工提供五年内归属的激励措施，以鼓励他们在被贝莱德收购后继续留任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hps-offers-incentives-to-retain-staff-after-sale-to-blackrock</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命亿万富翁 SpaceX 宇航员执掌 NASA</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-picks-jared-isaacman-as-nasa-administrator</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将提名金融科技亿万富翁、长期担任 SpaceX 宇航员的贾里德·艾萨克曼担任下一任 NASA 局长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-picks-jared-isaacman-as-nasa-administrator</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国关闭俄罗斯加密货币富豪网络，转移寡头数十亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方表示，他们已经关闭了俄罗斯网络，该网络通过在欧洲、中东和南美洲交换现金和加密货币，为寡头、街头帮派和间谍转移数十亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/crypto-rich-russian-networks-moving-oligarch-billions-shut-down-by-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰瑟枪和马斯克激励的薪酬方案让 Axon 首席执行官成为亿万富翁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/tasers-and-musk-inspired-pay-package-make-axon-ceo-a-billionaire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Axon Enterprise Inc. 的 CEO 薪酬方案模仿了埃隆·马斯克在特斯拉公司的激励措施，采取了高风险、高回报的策略。现在马斯克和 Axon 联合创始人里克·史密斯还有另一个共同点：他们都是亿万富翁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/tasers-and-musk-inspired-pay-package-make-axon-ceo-a-billionaire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
